Edge Cases:

| Case                  | Handling                                        |
| :-------------------- | :---------------------------------------------- |
| Initial focus         | Button gets focus, menu items are `tabindex="-1"` |
| Tab key               | Closes dropdown and moves focus out             |
| Shift+Tab             | Closes dropdown and moves focus out             |
| Mouse click on item   | Default link behavior, dropdown remains open (can be closed if desired) |

**Interview tip:** Discuss the importance of ARIA attributes (`aria-haspopup`, `aria-expanded`, `role="menu"`, `role="menuitem"`) for screen reader accessibility.

